eceived_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T21:53:48Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4339395454\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843#issuecomment-4339395454\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843\",\"id\":4339395454,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABAqXrfg\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T22:00:19Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-28T22:00:19Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` with `test_generation_failed`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2843-library-new-request-servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521-1893b4f1\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the handoff into scaffold/test generation, not artifact discovery itself. `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log` and `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log` show `discoverArtifactMetadata` completed with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` and `EXIT_CODE: 0`, and it produced `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json`. That discovery output only contains a description plus `N/A` for `source-code-url`, `repository-url`, `test-code-url`, and `documentation-url`, and the same logs also contain `ERROR codex_core::session: failed to record rollout items: thread 019dd615-8cdc-79a3-952a-ad411484f9f9 not found`.\\n\\nThere is no generated test or metadata output for this coordinate after discovery: no `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, no `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, and no `stats/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/stats.json`, so metrics and dynamic-access coverage are unavailable.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`\\n- `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log`\\n- `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. From the preserved branch, manually scaffold `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/` and `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, likely by adapting the existing servlet API coverage in `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/servlet-api/2.5-20081211/`.\\n2. Verify or replace the discovered artifact URLs/description if better exact-version sources can be found, then run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521`.\\n3. Once the tests exist, generate stats for the coordinate so coverage can be reviewed.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4339395454/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":24967172382,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAuy3ws8AAAAF0CjRHg\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/24967172382\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.gith