":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T20:45:03Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4361583338\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843#issuecomment-4361583338\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843\",\"id\":4361583338,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABA_h66g\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T20:51:17Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-01T20:51:17Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` with workflow status `failure`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2843-library-new-request-servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521-e3bc8dd8\\n\\nThe most likely failure point was test generation after artifact discovery completed. In `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`, the discovery step found that Maven Central only exposes the main JAR and POM for this coordinate and returned 404s for the version-matched `-sources.jar`, `-tests.jar`, and `-javadoc.jar`; the generated `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json` therefore ended up with `\\\"source-code-url\\\": \\\"N/A\\\"` and `\\\"test-code-url\\\": \\\"N/A\\\"`. No generated library files were produced for this coordinate (`metadata/servletapi/servletapi/index.json`, `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521`, and `stats/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521` are all absent), and run metrics are unavailable, which suggests the workflow stopped before it could synthesize tests or metadata from usable source context.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`\\n- `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n- Find a trustworthy version-specific source or test reference for Servlet 2.4, or decide to hand-author tests directly from the API/spec and binary JAR.\\n- Use existing servlet API support in this repo, such as `org.mortbay.jetty:servlet-api:2.5-20081211` or `javax.servlet:javax.servlet-api:3.1.0`, as a baseline for manual test and metadata creation.\\n- Re-run the `library-new-request` flow after adding usable source/test context or manual scaffolding.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4361583338/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25082542482,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAuy3ws8AAAAF1wk5kg\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25082542