{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_27","type":"command_execution","command":"/usr/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' /tmp/rhei-issue-comments/2843.json\"","aggregated_output":"[{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4339395454\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843#issuecomment-4339395454\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843\",\"id\":4339395454,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABAqXrfg\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T22:00:19Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-28T22:00:19Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` with `test_generation_failed`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2843-library-new-request-servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521-1893b4f1\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the handoff into scaffold/test generation, not artifact discovery itself. `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log` and `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log` show `discoverArtifactMetadata` completed with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` and `EXIT_CODE: 0`, and it produced `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json`. That discovery output only contains a description plus `N/A` for `source-code-url`, `repository-url`, `test-code-url`, and `documentation-url`, and the same logs also contain `ERROR codex_core::session: failed to record rollout items: thread 019dd615-8cdc-79a3-952a-ad411484f9f9 not found`.\\n\\nThere is no generated test or metadata output for this coordinate after discovery: no `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, no `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, and no `stats/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/stats.json`, so metrics and dynamic-access coverage are unavailable.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`\\n- `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log`\\n- `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. From the preserved branch, manually scaffold `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/` and `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521/`, likely by adapting the existing servlet API coverage in `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/servlet-api/2.5-20081211/`.\\n2. Verify or replace the discovered artifact URLs/description if better exact-version sources can be found, then run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521`.\\n3. Once the tests exist, generate stats for the coordinate so coverage can be reviewed.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4339395454/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4361583338\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843#issuecomment-4361583338\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843\",\"id\":4361583338,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABA_h66g\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T20:51:17Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-01T20:51:17Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` with workflow status `failure`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2843-library-new-request-servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521-e3bc8dd8\\n\\nThe most likely failure point was test generation after artifact discovery completed. In `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`, the discovery step found that Maven Central only exposes the main JAR and POM for this coordinate and returned 404s for the version-matched `-sources.jar`, `-tests.jar`, and `-javadoc.jar`; the generated `build/discovered-artifact-metadata/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.json` therefore ended up with `\\\"source-code-url\\\": \\\"N/A\\\"` and `\\\"test-code-url\\\": \\\"N/A\\\"`. No generated library files were produced for this coordinate (`metadata/servletapi/servletapi/index.json`, `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521`, and `stats/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521` are all absent), and run metrics are unavailable, which suggests the workflow stopped before it could synthesize tests or metadata from usable source context.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log`\\n- `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n- Find a trustworthy version-specific source or test reference for Servlet 2.4, or decide to hand-author tests directly from the API/spec and binary JAR.\\n- Use existing servlet API support in this repo, such as `org.mortbay.jetty:servlet-api:2.5-20081211` or `javax.servlet:javax.servlet-api:3.1.0`, as a baseline for manual test and metadata creation.\\n- Re-run the `library-new-request` flow after adding usable source/test context or manual scaffolding.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4361583338/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365990251\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843#issuecomment-4365990251\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2843\",\"id\":4365990251,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDu5aw\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:52:09Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:52:09Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `library-new-request` job failed for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` with workflow status `failure`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2843-library-new-request-servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521-8e212ec0\\n\\nThe preserved evidence suggests `discoverArtifactMetadata` succeeded, but the run failed immediately afterward during test scaffolding/generation. `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log` ends with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` for `:discoverArtifactMetadata` and shows the discovered metadata falling back to Apache Tomcat 5.0 archived sources plus `\\\"test-code-url\\\": \\\"N/A\\\"`, but there is no generated `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521`, `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521`, `stats/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521`, or scratch run metrics, so dynamic-access coverage is unavailable.\\n\\nThis also looks like a relocation/alias case rather than a brand-new API: the published POM for `servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` relocates to `javax.servlet:servlet-api:2.4-20040521`, and the jar entry list matches the already-supported Servlet 2.4 artifact in this repo. A useful reference baseline is `tests/src/javax.servlet/servlet-api/2.4`, `metadata/javax.servlet/servlet-api/2.4/reachability-metadata.json`, and `stats/javax.servlet/servlet-api/2.4/execution-metrics.json` (7/7 dynamic-access calls covered).\\n\\nPlease inspect `human-intervention-logs/servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521/discover-artifact-metadata/discover_artifact_metadata.log` first. If you still have the failed workspace locally, also inspect `build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/servletapi-servletapi-2.4-20040521.log`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Treat this as a relocated Servlet 2.4 alias and seed `metadata/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521` and `tests/src/servletapi/servletapi/2.4-20040521` from the existing `javax.servlet:servlet-api:2.4` support.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=servletapi:servletapi:2.4-20040521`.\\n3. If generation still needs source context, replace the archived-source fallback with a curated mapping based on the relocation target before retrying.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365990251/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null}]","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
